main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 358/79 is hereby amended as follows:
1. Article 12 (3) shall be replaced by the following:
'3. Before 1 April 1993, the Commission shall present to the European Parliament and the Council, in the light of experience gained, a report on the maximum sulphur dioxide content, together, where appropriate, with proposals on which the Council shall  act in accordance with the procedure laid down by Article 43 (2) of the Treaty before 1 September 1993.';
2. Article 16 (3) shall be replaced by the following:
'3. Before 1 April 1993, the Commission shall present to the European Parliament and the Council, in the light of experience gained, a report on the maximum sulphur dioxide content, together, where appropriate, with proposals on which the Council shall  act in accordance with the procedure laid down by Article 43 (2) of the Treaty before 1 September 1993.';
3. In Article 17 (3), '1 September 1992' shall be replaced by '1 September 1993'.
